import React from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'

function Contact() {
    return (
        <Container>
            <Header>
                <Text>
                    Get In Touch
                </Text>
            </Header>
            <Form>
                <FullName>
                    <Name>
                        <Input/>
                    </Name>
                    <Name>
                        <Input/>
                    </Name>
                </FullName>
                <Email>
                    <Input/>
                </Email>
                <Message>
                    <Textarea></Textarea>
                </Message>
                <Button>
                    Submit
                </Button>
            </Form>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default Contact

const Container = styled.div`
min-height: 600px;
    
    &::-webkit-scrollbar {
        display: inline;
  }
`
